text = "[ul]
[b]Weekly Income:[/b] You receive [color=green]$150[/color] every week.

[b]Budgets:[/b] Set limits for Food & Vet to control spending. Budgets reset every 7 days.

[b]Emergency Savings:[/b] Start with $200. This fund is used [b]automatically[/b] if you can't afford essential items (Food/Vet).

[color=yellow]Warning:[/color] Relying on savings is risky! Keep a buffer for real emergencies.
[/ul]"

